components.name: Run CTAS
components.description: Creates analytics tables from raw data using CTAS pattern with data validation and atomic table replacement. Each table task depends on the previous table task completion and implements zero-row validation.

upstream_policy.description: Each table task depends on the previous table task completion.

name.constraints: Must be a unique identifier for the pipeline

batch_window.description: Batch window parameter name (e.g., ds, execution_date)

partitioning.description: Data partitioning strategy (e.g., daily, hourly, monthly)

depends_on_past.description: Whether execution depends on previous run success

table_params.description: Dictionary containing schema, table name, and SQL query
table_params.constraints: Must contain keys: schema, table_name, sql_query

snowflake_conn.constraints: Must be a valid Snowflake connection ID

sinks: Analytics tables in Snowflake schema: analytics.mau_summary
